dm_omfg
====================

by InsomniaC1984

--------------------

NOTE:

This map is FREEWARE!!!
Please feel free to host/distribute this map on your site/web space,
as long as it is not used in any commertial way
(e.g. as part of a missionpack or so).
However this .zip archive MUST remain intact and you
are not allowed to claim this work as your own. If you do host this
file, please email me the link to it...
I'd like to know... :P

--------------------

Contact :

psychodad270484@aol.com

--------------------
                                                                               


Install Info:

Extract the .tip into your C:\Steam\SteamApps\[nickname]\
folder and run cs:s.
The package contains the following files:
dm_omfg.bsp
dm_omfg.txt
arrow_blue.vmt
arrow_red.vmt
insooo1.vmt
insooo2.vmt
arrow_blue.vtf
arrow_red.vtf
insooo1.vtf
insooo2.vtf

note: the folderstucture should remain intact to run the map properbly...

--------------------


additional notes:
+included:
  dm_omfg.res
  dm_omfg.nav

+map-features:
 non-bulletproof/breakable obstacles
 jumppads
 teleporters
